      <description>Learn how to escalate privileges in an Active Directory environment by exploiting SMB guest write access and GPO abuse. This walkthrough covers NTLM hash capturing with Responder, ntlm-theft, and leveraging SharpGPOAbuse to gain local admin rights on a Windows Domain Controller.</description>
